actionConfiguration.body:
UPDATE FPPTable SET
		FPP = '{{update_form.fieldState.FPP.isVisible ? update_form.formData.FPP : update_form.sourceData.FPP}}',
		Supplier = '{{update_form.fieldState.Supplier.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Supplier : update_form.sourceData.Supplier}}',
    Expiry = '{{update_form.fieldState.Expiry.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Expiry : update_form.sourceData.Expiry}}',
		Coupe = '{{update_form.fieldState.Coupe.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Coupe : update_form.sourceData.Coupe}}',
		Harvestor = '{{update_form.fieldState.Harvestor.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Harvestor : update_form.sourceData.Harvestor}}',
		Claim = '{{update_form.fieldState.Claim.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Claim : update_form.sourceData.Claim}}',
		Certificate = '{{update_form.fieldState.Certificate.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Certificate : update_form.sourceData.Certificate}}',
		Holder = '{{update_form.fieldState.Holder.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Holder : update_form.sourceData.Holder}}',
		Claim_From = '{{update_form.fieldState.Claim_From.isVisible ? update_form.formData.Claim_From : update_form.sourceData.Claim_From}}'
WHERE Operations = '{{fpp_data_table.selectedRow.Operations}}';
